Title: Designates dog control officers of the village of Holley, named by the village board as constables, as peace officers
Summary: Designates dog control officers of the village of Holley, named by the village board as constables, as peace officers.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the criminal procedure law, in relation to designating as peace officers dog control officers of the village of Holley
